               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsān maḥyawi “The Life-Giving Homily” (fols. 3ra) 
 I-1)
                     Introductory prayer (fol.3ra-va) 
 I-2) Reading for Monday, Compline
                     (nǝwam) (fols. 3va-18ra) 
 I-3) Reading for Tuesday, Matins (manfaqa lelit)
                     (fols.18ra-31vb) 
 I-4) Reading for Wednesday, Lauds (nagh) (fols.
                     31vb-42rb) 
 I-5) Reading for Thursday, Terce (śalastu säʿat) (fols.
                     42rb-55rb) 
 I-6) Reading for Friday, Sext (qätr) (fols. 55rb-67va)
                     I-7) Reading for Saturday, None (täsaʿtu säʿat) (fols. 67va-79va)
 I-8)
                     Reading for Sunday, Vespers (śark) (fols. 79va-94va)
 II) Malkǝʾa madḫane
                     ʿālam “Image of the Saviour of the World” (fols. 94vb-100rb).</summary>
