               <provenance>A few names are mentioned in the supplication
                     formulas: Gabra Māryām (e.g., 3va, 18rb, 30ra,
                     39rb, 40va, 77vb, 89rb), his mother Walatta Ḥǝywat (e.g., 8vb, 31vb, 65va), his wife Walatta Yoḥannǝs (e.g., 12ra, 29ra, 38ra, 42rb, 55rb, 76va, 89rb), his late
                     father ʾabuna Walda ʿAbiyä ʾƎgziʾ (49rb, 83ra, 89rb), and his children Gabra Yoḥannǝs
                     and Walatta Tǝnśāʾe (87va). Most of the names are
                     repeated in the concluding supplication formula (94va).</provenance></history>
